Dear ,

**This refers to yourrequest for a Personal Comprehensive Assessment and Initial Consultation (PCAIC).**

Thank you for securing the agreement andyour initial payment.In order to continue the assessment and to provide you with the most effective service, we will need you to complete the attachedquestionnaire.

### PROFILEQUESTIONNAIRE
Please complete the correct profile questionnaire designated for you by clicking the link below.

Wewill notify you ofournext steps once we receive and assess your documentation.Please reply directly to this email thread when you have completed thequestionnaire.We would appreciate it if you could send your answers in a timely manner.

On behalf ofDuque Immigration Services Canada Inc., we would like to thank you again for choosing us as your Canadian immigration representative.Should you have anyquestionsor concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us @ (204) 339-2522.

Furthermore, we encourage you tofollow/like our Facebook page (below) as we will needto communicate with you at all times.Please note that we have a 24 hour processing service on our Facebook page.

We will notify you of the next steps once we received and assessed your documentation. If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us.

**IMPORTANT**:Please be advised that in order to avoid miscommunication or delay in processing, please copy everyone on this email thread or click REPLY ALL on every correspondence.

Best Regards,

Processing Team | Duque Immigration Services Inc.

Unit 2 - 2536 Main Street, Winnipeg, Manitoba , Canada RV2 4Y2
